<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
        .success { background: #d1fae5; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 12px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>✅ Password Changed Successfully</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
        
        <div class="success">
            Your password for {{appName}} has been changed successfully.
        </div>

        <p><strong>Changed at:</strong> {{changedAt}}</p>

        <p>If you made this change, no further action is required.</p>

        <p>If you did NOT change your password:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Contact support immediately</li>
            <li>Your account may have been compromised</li>
            <li>We'll help you secure your account</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2025 {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

